# Protected Files

NEVER modify these files without explicit approval:

- `packages/excalidraw/scene/Renderer.ts` — render pipeline orchestrator
- `packages/excalidraw/renderer/staticScene.ts` — static canvas rendering
- `packages/excalidraw/renderer/interactiveScene.ts` — interactive canvas rendering
- `packages/excalidraw/data/restore.ts` — file format compatibility
- `packages/excalidraw/actions/manager.tsx` — action system dispatcher
- `packages/excalidraw/types.ts` — core types (AppState, etc.)
- `packages/element/src/Scene.ts` — element store and scene management

Changes to protected files require:

1. Full understanding of downstream dependencies
2. Running complete test suite (`vitest run`)
3. Manual QA verification

## How to verify

- `git diff --name-only` — check none of the protected files appear in uncommitted changes
- `git diff HEAD~1 --name-only` — check last commit didn't modify protected files without approval
- If a protected file was modified: `yarn test:all` must pass, and `yarn build:packages` must succeed